title: 30 Pcs Birthday Invitations for Girls, Party Invites, Party Invites for Girls, Pink Butterfly Themed party Invitation Cards for Kids Birthday Decorations
features: 【Complete 30-Piece Invitation Set】: This value pack includes 30 beautifully designed pink butterfly invitations, Each card ready for handwritten party details. Perfect for birthday party planning with enough invitations for the whole class or neighborhood friends.

【Premium Quality Materials】: Made from high quality cardstock with a luxurious matte finish that resists fingerprints and smudges, wrinkle-resistant paper that ensures the vibrant prints stay true and beautiful, even after long-term storage. Pink color remains vibrant without fading, and the delicate butterfly design appeals specifically to young girls' tastes.

【Customizable Party Essential】: Each blank invitation provides ample space to write party details (date, time, location, RSVP). The gender-neutral wording makes them suitable for various party themes beyond butterflies. Coordinating envelopes save time and complete the polished look when mailing to guests.

【Time-Saving Party Solution】: Designed by party professionals to eliminate DIY stress - just fill in details and send! The elegant design reduces need for additional decorations when used as part of party table displays. Comes packaged in a protective cellophane sleeve to prevent bending during storage.

【Perfect for Special Celebrations】: Ideal for: girls' birthday parties, butterfly-themed events, princess parties, or garden celebrations. Also great for baby showers, bridal showers, or tea parties when a feminine touch is desired. Makes party planning easier for busy parents and event organizers.
